  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the number of cases, the average cycle time, and the material group text for purchase order items. It is performed on the 'defaultview-124' table. The number of cases is calculated by counting the 'CASE_ID' column. The average cycle time is calculated by subtracting the last end time for the 'Create Goods Receipt' event from the last end time for the 'Receive Advanced Shipment Notice (ASN)' event. The material group text is selected from the 'PO Item Material Group Text' column. The results are grouped by the third column and ordered in descending order based on the number of cases. The query returns a maximum of 50 rows."
